aces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cf1d50f0e59fe2d76910a66059f0b7615d8053a","tid":2387240,"uid":144626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T07:45:41.000Z","msg":"咁又點，最少可以貢獻當地"},{"pid":"69e8b14ff0f616819e220fb875b56b283621c5fc","tid":2387240,"uid":161726,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T07:46:11.000Z","msg":"蘇格蘭獨立運動如火如荼，威爾斯也正在有樣學樣。香港人如果定居在蘇格蘭或者威爾斯，幾年後這些地方脫離聯合王國（United Kingdom），會不會變成蘇格蘭公民或威爾斯公民<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇聽過乜野叫Good Friday Agreement?<br />\n人地一定有得比你揀,邊度好似係大陸老粗野蠻"},{"pid":"b2cbc2f94071a42f4a21ed5b1d7f704d990f634f","tid":2387240,"uid":52695,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T07:46:41.000Z","msg":"攞黎7<br />\n人地講獨冇問題<br />\n港獨就國安又拉又鎖"},{"pid":"ed690a41327ff0a00df51e36ede58f182067ce3e","tid":2387240,"uid":225798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T07:47:51.000Z","msg":"點解唔得"},{"pid":"d409c7cc349688f87d2e55fd8044b9af705df9f5","tid":2387240,"uid":14422,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T07:48:47.000Z","msg":"7月1日就榮升香港第一夫人的唐青儀，在梁振英參選之前作風低調，外界對她的了解不多。本報追查唐青儀的身世，發現她年輕時曾跟隨英籍親戚改姓「Higgins」，其間成功入籍英國，婚後又改回中文姓名。有律師估計在英國讀書的唐青儀被英籍親戚收養而入英籍，藉此獲減免學費。唐青儀和特首辦都拒回應改姓原因。"},{"pid":"fbb52d27792f230a7a57e36e83aad0a24eac5e8a","tid":2387240,"uid":48362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T07:49:26.000Z","msg":"689 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"363bff4efc